    <section id="id1166970226048">
      <title>MAIN DIRECTIONS AND INTERMEDIATE DIRECTIONS</title>
      <para id="id7178934">Direction</para>
      <para id="id8156170">It is important for every person to know in what direction he is moving. Just think of what the pilot of an aeroplane, a seafarer or a hiker in the mountains would do if they could not determine direction. Yes, they would all get lost and end up in the wrong places.</para>
      <section id="id2984418">
