        <para id="id1166969455440">Identify points A/B/C/D on the playground.</para>
        <para id="id1166981455600">Hide prizes at the end of each group’s treasure hunt. The field must be prepared beforehand. Divide your class into four groups. Each group starts at a point indicated beforehand and searches for their treasure by following the required route.</para>
