      <section id="id3043848">
        <title>To determine intermediate directions [LO 1.4]</title>
        <para id="id1166979398468">Between the four main directions we must therefore identify four additional or intermediate directions: </para>
        <para id="id6895180">Now complete the following:</para>
        <para id="id1166981243332">1. Between South and East we have:………………………………………………</para>
        <para id="id6427872">2. Between North and West we have:……………………………………………...</para>
        <para id="id1166970706398">3. Between South and West we have:……………………………………………..</para>
        <para id="id7613172">First mentioning North or South and then adding the other direction therefore give the names of the intermediate directions.</para>
      </section>
